name: Jimmy Connors Pro Tennis Tour [SNES]
description: Jimmy Connors Pro Tennis Tour (ジミーコナーズのプロテニスツアー, Jimī Konāzu no Puro Tenisu Tsuā) is a video game developed by Blue Byte and released in 1993. It is the second video game to feature Jimmy Connors after his name was used for the 1993 game, Jimmy Connors Tennis.
